We examined the Spearman (rank) correlation of the expression of the significantly differentially expressed splicing factors (when comparing postnatal to fetal muscle samples) with the inclusion \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
